WEBVTT

00:02.435 --> 00:03.569
Good morning, Lemon.

00:03.637 --> 00:05.238
Ugh. I hate January.

00:05.304 --> 00:06.905
It's dark and freezing,

00:06.973 --> 00:08.508
and everyone's wearing bulky coats.

00:08.574 --> 00:10.575
You can do some serious subway flirting

00:10.644 --> 00:12.062
before you realize the guy is homeless.

00:14.840 --> 00:16.131
Work is awful.

00:16.199 --> 00:18.295
Everyone's snippy and tense.

00:18.364 --> 00:20.191
Well, the lack of sun
makes people depressed.

00:20.259 --> 00:22.189
It's called seasonal affective disorder.

00:22.256 --> 00:25.012
Oh, is that where
the word "sad" comes from?

00:25.047 --> 00:27.107
What?
You think "sad" is an acronym

00:27.173 --> 00:28.374
invented by psychologists?

00:28.440 --> 00:30.677
I've been stuck inside
playing online boggle.

00:30.744 --> 00:31.984
It's messing with my head.

00:32.054 --> 00:34.688
Star, rats, arts, tars.

00:37.027 --> 00:38.528
It's from Nancy.

00:38.597 --> 00:41.802
She said she's in line
behind the female Larry Bird.

00:41.871 --> 00:42.803
Oh, God.

00:42.871 --> 00:44.071
There's a photo.

00:44.138 --> 00:45.371
Oh, come on.

00:45.440 --> 00:47.777
How is female Larry Bird
holding hands with a guy?

00:47.844 --> 00:49.246
What am I doing wrong?

00:50.316 --> 00:51.716
What's that for?

00:51.784 --> 00:53.820
I'm telling Nancy that
I'm with female Kevin McHale.

00:53.888 --> 00:55.857
So what's going on
with you and Nancy, anyway?

00:55.925 --> 00:58.194
We're just friends.
It's platonic.

00:58.262 --> 00:59.330
I have elaborate fantasies

00:59.398 --> 01:01.264
of her husband dying in a boat explosion.

01:01.332 --> 01:03.199
But she's getting divorced, right?

01:03.266 --> 01:04.434
Well, she hasn't mentioned it.

01:04.501 --> 01:05.602
It's not the sort of thing

01:05.671 --> 01:07.371
you discuss by text or email.

01:07.439 --> 01:09.538
Well, this is my stop.

01:09.606 --> 01:12.876
Stop. Pots.
Tops. Opts. Post.

01:12.944 --> 01:14.044
Morning, Kenneth.

01:14.113 --> 01:15.447
Good morning, Miss Lemon.

01:15.515 --> 01:16.647
I'm sorry.

01:16.715 --> 01:18.682
I didn't mean to snap at you.

01:18.749 --> 01:21.218
I've got winter madness.

01:21.285 --> 01:23.954
Lutz, do the right thing.

01:24.022 --> 01:25.355
What's going on?

01:25.424 --> 01:27.257
It's Lutz's turn
to pick where we eat today.

01:27.324 --> 01:29.226
Oh, boy.
Lutz, don't do this.

01:29.294 --> 01:30.863
It's my turn to pick.

01:30.929 --> 01:32.296
I'm the picker.

01:32.364 --> 01:33.931
Lutz, look at me.

01:33.999 --> 01:35.466
It's a long year.

01:35.533 --> 01:36.701
Think of the group.

01:36.767 --> 01:38.702
- Subway.
- I hope you die!

01:38.771 --> 01:41.272
Are you out of your mind?

01:41.340 --> 01:43.075
Whoa, you guys.
Calm down.

01:43.143 --> 01:45.378
I know we're all tired and cranky,

01:45.445 --> 01:47.947
but we just got to get
to the end of the season.

01:48.015 --> 01:49.315
And, hey, who knows?

01:49.383 --> 01:52.787
Maybe some people
won't be coming back next year.

01:52.855 --> 01:55.123
I don't care.
Worth it.

01:55.190 --> 01:56.891
I hate the new guy.

01:56.958 --> 01:57.925
Loser.

